data.description: This stunning property sits on nearly 10 acres just outside the Seneca city limits! Boasting 5 bedrooms and a basement featuring a convenient kitchenette, 2 beds, and 1 bath, perfect for entertaining and/or accommodating guests. The basement also offers a heated/cooled 18x22 1-car garage, providing additional storage space or a workshop area. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with two water heaters and a pressure tank just 6 years old, along with an HVAC system installed in 2014 and a roof that's only less than 5 years old. Modern conveniences includes most appliances less than 10 years old, as well as 2 washer/dryer hookups. Solid wood doors and tall trim add an elegant touch throughout the home, while a practical mudroom keeps living areas organized. Outside, a 40 x 60 shop with 4 overhead 12x12 doors awaits, perfect for housing vehicles or indulging in hobbies. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this remarkable property your own!
